{"tid":2044581,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局提醒大家","createTime":"2020-05-31T07:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T09:39:10.000Z","uid":272122,"like":566,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"a698db10b0cd1181c102a66c3760c4f6bd1d29b9","tid":2044581,"uid":272122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"金管局今日留意到有謠言指香港會實施外匯管制。<br />\n<br />\n金管局呼籲市民切勿跟車太貼，務必小心核實訊息以防炒車！<br />\n<br />\n資金自由流動和港幣自由兌換將一如既往受到《基本法》第112條的保障。<br />\n<br />\n香港財政及金融系統實力底子深厚，有能力抵禦衝擊：<br />\n<br />\n▪️4400億美元外滙儲備（達貨幣基礎 2 倍以上）<br />\n▪️銀行體系資本雄厚 （20%資本充足比率）<br />\n▪️流動資金充裕（流動覆蓋比率160 %）<br />\n▪️資產質素良好（壞帳率僅0.6%）<br />\n<br />\n金管局重申不需要也無計劃改變行之有效的聯匯制度，我們有能力、資源及決心維持香港貨幣及金融穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EjSEXj3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjSEXj3.jpg&h=203e3575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192c7325a912c6a71c6e98efaa1175a56c47dec5","tid":2044581,"uid":31237,"like":212,"dislike":2,"score":210,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:56:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">基本法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5524049bb52e6c5e1cfbb2f6a4affe9faad20582","tid":2044581,"uid":8441,"like":226,"dislike":2,"score":224,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:57:18.000Z","msg":"資產質素良好（壞帳率僅0.6%）<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園債咪又要政府bail out <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873d77509d35200832239f7d6dcc6c00e6978120","tid":2044581,"uid":289259,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"192c7325a912c6a71c6e98efaa1175a56c47dec5","tid":2044581,"uid":31237,"like":212,"dislike":2,"score":210,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:56:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">基本法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"仲有既咩？"},{"pid":"1e578